The paper discusses a scalable optimization algorithm for coreset selection in graphs, which is a common problem in machine learning and data analysis. The paper also discusses the estimation error and selection costs, which are important topics in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), social and information networks (cs.SI), and information theory (cs.IT). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
